<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: part_connected_terminals_definition
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part_mim.part_connected_terminals_definition">
<p>

A <b>part_connected_terminals_definition</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> that implements the
ARM concept of  <express_ref linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part:arm:Functional_assignment_to_part_arm.Part_connected_terminals_definition"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: part_connected_terminals_definition.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part_mim.part_connected_terminals_definition.wr:WR1">
The <b>part_connected_terminals_definition</b> shall relate to at least two instances of
 <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_usage_view:mim:Assembly_module_usage_view_mim.assembly_module_terminal"/>,  <express_ref linkend="Bare_die:mim:Bare_die_mim.bare_die_terminal"/>,  <express_ref linkend="Interconnect_module_usage_view:mim:Interconnect_module_usage_view_mim.interconnect_module_terminal"/>,
 <express_ref linkend="Package:mim:Package_mim.package_terminal"/>, or  <express_ref linkend="Packaged_part_black_box_model:mim:Packaged_part_black_box_model_mim.packaged_part_terminal"/> to specify a 'member connected
terminal'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
UR: part_connected_terminals_definition.UR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part_mim.part_connected_terminals_definition.ur:UR1">
The name shall be unique.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part_mim.functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_constraint">
<p>

The <b>functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_constraint</b> rule 
constrains the related and relating  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> of a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>
when it is used as a functional terminal allocation.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_constraint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part_mim.functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_constraint.wr:WR1">
IF  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>.name = 'functional terminal allocation' THEN 
SELF.<express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/> shall be a  <express_ref linkend="Functional_usage_view:mim:Functional_usage_view_mim.functional_unit_terminal_definition"/> 
with a description = 'scalar terminal'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_constraint.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part_mim.functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_constraint.wr:WR2">
IF  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>.name = 'functional terminal allocation' THEN 
SELF.<express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/> shall be an ( <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_usage_view:mim:Assembly_module_usage_view_mim.assembly_module_terminal"/>) 
( <express_ref linkend="Bare_die:mim:Bare_die_mim.bare_die_terminal"/>) ( <express_ref linkend="Interconnect_module_usage_view:mim:Interconnect_module_usage_view_mim.interconnect_module_terminal"/>) 
( <express_ref linkend="Packaged_part_black_box_model:mim:Packaged_part_black_box_model_mim.packaged_part_terminal"/>).
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part_mim.functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint">
<p>

The <b>functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains 
 <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> population members, that fill the role of ARM
<express_ref linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part:arm:Functional_assignment_to_part_arm.Functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment"/>, so that the combination of ARM
<express_ref linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part:arm:Functional_assignment_to_part_arm.Functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment.functional_usage_view_terminal"/> and ARM <express_ref linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part:arm:Functional_assignment_to_part_arm.Functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment.physical_usage_view_terminal"/> attributes
shall be unique within the population.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_assignment_to_part_mim.functional_usage_view_to_part_terminal_assignment_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> with a description of 'functional terminal allocation'
that references a common  <express_ref linkend="Functional_usage_view:mim:Functional_usage_view_mim.functional_unit_terminal_definition"/> with a name of 'scalar terminal'
through its <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/> attribute must have a unique reference to either an
 <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_usage_view:mim:Assembly_module_usage_view_mim.assembly_module_terminal"/>,  <express_ref linkend="Bare_die:mim:Bare_die_mim.bare_die_terminal"/>,  <express_ref linkend="Interconnect_module_usage_view:mim:Interconnect_module_usage_view_mim.interconnect_module_terminal"/> 
or  <express_ref linkend="Packaged_part_black_box_model:mim:Packaged_part_black_box_model_mim.packaged_part_terminal"/> through its <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/> attribute.
</ext_description>

</ext_descriptions>
